column5: Hey guys  I'm heading up to simcoe in the morning for some perch, anyone care to hook up?
Just my little one, i ripped my knee up in mexico, care to join?
good luck, think I'm going to enter the tournie on kempenfelt bay tomorrow

charity event, costs $80.00 per hole, runs from noon til 3 p.m. starting at the southshore centre on lakeshore drive. $ goes to a Gilda's Club which they are starting up in Barrie.  I had a friend last year who won $100 last year on a dink perch because so few fish got caught!  Biggest perch last year apparently won an aluminum boat.
Wife read in the paper...Prizes in excess of $50,000 this weekend.  For more info..  www.gbhba.on.ca
